---
title: Pan-Fried Chicken Thighs with Stovetop Green Bean Casserole
description: Green bean casserole is a retro classic no one can deny! Tonight we've paired it with tender, juicy pan-fried chicken thighs and roasted russets for a full-on week-day feast!
